{"tid":124789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警判刑】曾偉雄指心情沉重：同事執勤時「可能犯咗啲錯誤」","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T07:01:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bddde3f53a20eecc8238947672656f2bb0258f14","tid":124789,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170218/large/1487381623_7a6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170218%2Flarge%2F1487381623_7a6c.jpg&h=1938f59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七名警員因為毆打前公民黨成員曾健超罪成，全部判監兩年兼不得假釋，更可能被革職失去長俸退休金；2014年佔領運動期間任警務處處長、現已退休的前「一哥」曾偉雄接受《明報》訪問時指心情沉重，強調如7名警員上訴，其他同袍會全力協助。<br />\n<br />\n被問及對判刑的看法，曾偉雄指自己與很多同事﹙警員﹚心情均非常沉重，因同事在執勤期間「可能犯咗啲錯誤。」對於警隊沒為警員執勤期間犯刑責認錯是否姑息犯事警員，曾回應「不要再講這個問題」，又指應向「現任嗰啲」查詢，自己只是以市民身份回應。<br />\n2014年佔領運動期間，前「一哥」曾偉雄曾向警員稱「你哋冇做錯到」，接受傳媒訪問時形容警察如慈母般保護學生。"},{"pid":"7924350f46d36b2ced0b73249c1a519811188c71","tid":124789,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"你哋冇做錯到"},{"pid":"e2b4211af9fe197b5cfe084318b5a3a184cdae5f","tid":124789,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e774d243230c8570b664a9021e295d80f0852df3","tid":124789,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"喂又話冇做錯？"},{"pid":"68b7bb4245c726fbc18497d2a7fa8eb294609018","tid":124789,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"點止犯錯，直頭犯法添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e479b42b19e889c38703f4adafa69867dfb2c35","tid":124789,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.g